OL,6,FThat figure is up by #382 million when
OL,7,Fit was last analysed in 2022.
OL,9,FOf those who ended up with an
OL,10,Faccidental subscription, 40% said it
OL,11,Frenewed automatically without their
OL,12,Fknowledge.
OL,14,FThis was followed by 39% who took out
OL,15,Fa subscription for a free trial but
OL,16,Fforgot to cancel it later, while 24%
OL,17,Fthought they were making a one-off
OL,18,Fpurchase.
