OL,6,FA clamp down on the practice by the
OL,7,Fgovernment in the upcoming Digital
OL,8,FMarkets, Competition and Consumer Bill
OL,9,Fis being called for by the charity.
OL,11,FCitizens Advice wants to see consumers
OL,12,Fgiven the choice over whether their
OL,13,Fsubscriptions are subject to automatic
OL,14,Frenewal, and over whether they want to
OL,15,Fcontinue to use a subscription service
OL,16,Fat the end of a free trial.
