OL,3,C'Unacceptable' subscription traps
OL,4,Ccosting consumers #688m per year
OL,6,FCitizens Advice chief executive Dame
OL,7,FClare Moriarty said: "With budgets
OL,8,Fincreasingly squeezed and living costs
OL,9,Foften exceeding the amount people have
OL,10,Fcoming in each month, it's vital
OL,11,Fconsumers feel in control of their
OL,12,Fspending.
OL,14,F"Companies relying on people
OL,15,Fforgetting to cancel at the end of a
OL,16,Ffree trial is an unacceptable business
OL,17,Fmodel that exploits busy, cash-
OL,18,Fstrapped consumers.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/8
