OL,6,FA Department for Business and Trade
OL,7,Fspokesman said: "We know it's
OL,8,Ffrustrating to find out you're still
OL,9,Fpaying for something you weren't
OL,10,Fexpecting.
OL,12,F"That is why we are delivering
OL,13,Flegislation this year that will ensure
OL,14,Fconsumers have clear information about
OL,15,Ftheir subscription terms and can exit
OL,16,Funwanted subscriptions easily, giving
OL,17,Fthem peace of mind and greater control
OL,18,Fof their cash."
OL,20,FOpinium surveyed 3,000 UK adults
OL,21,Fbetween January 26 and February 1.
